The article is a statement by Melania and Donald Trump expressing their condolences on the passing of Billy Graham. They describe Graham as an American hero and "God's Ambassador" who had a profound impact on the world through his ministry and his message of God's love. The article also mentions Graham's wife, Ruth, and the international team and institution he built to continue spreading Christ's message. Melania and Donald Trump express their gratitude for knowing Graham and his family and state that Christians and people of all faiths will miss him.